---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 32
By: Marsilio Ficino
Tags:
  - Creation=Simultaneity of the Divine Act
  - Discernment-Truth=The Eye Of Eternity-Supreme Center=Omniscience
    and Omnipresence
Comment: |
  Here Ficino is referring to the creation of the Archetypes.
---
Since in God being and thinking are identical, the notion which God,
in thinking Himself, generates as an exact image of Himself, is
identical with God Himself.
